# Environment Variables for Railway Deployment

## Required Variables

### Database (PostgreSQL Required)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:port/database
# Note: Railway automatically provides this when you add a PostgreSQL service
# For local development, use a local PostgreSQL instance or cloud service

### Reown (WalletConnect)
NEXT_PUBLIC_REOWN_PROJECT_ID=your_reown_project_id
# Get this from https://dashboard.reown.com

### Application URL
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-app-name.railway.app
# Update this with your actual Railway domain
# For local: http://localhost:1337

### NextAuth (for session management)
NEXTAUTH_URL=https://your-app-name.railway.app
# Same as NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=your-random-secret-key-here
# Generate a random secret: openssl rand -base64 32

## Optional Variables

### Node Environment
NODE_ENV=production
